# =====================================================================
# DOCKER IGNORE FILE FOR YOUCERT PROJECT
# Optimizes Docker build by excluding unnecessary files
# =====================================================================

# =====================================================================
# PYTHON & VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENTS
# =====================================================================
