# *.woff2

# =====================================================================
# NODE MODULES (if using npm/yarn for frontend)
# =====================================================================
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
package-lock.json
yarn.lock

# =====================================================================
# WHAT GETS INCLUDED (Should NOT be in .dockerignore)
# =====================================================================
# ✅ youcert/ directory (main application code)
# ✅ requirements.txt (pip dependencies)
# ✅ run.py (Flask entry point)
# ✅ config.py (configuration - sanitize secrets!)
# ✅ Static assets (.png, .jpg, .ttf if needed)
# ✅ Templates (HTML files)
# =====================================================================

# =====================================================================
# NOTES FOR DEPLOYMENT
# =====================================================================
# 1. Secrets should ALWAYS be loaded from environment variables
# 2. Never include .env files in Docker images
# 3. Use Cloud Secret Manager for production secrets
# 4. Keep images small by excluding development/test files
# 5. Service account keys should be mounted at runtime, not baked in
# =====================================================================
